message.body: Hey, I have to stop up at rite aid quick before I head over. You need any last minute items?
###### and I both think you are very sweet for asking, but I'm all set :)
Ok, see you in a few. I expect CHEEK KISSES! ;)
Very very buzzed but I wouldn't say drunk.
Sorry if I sent mixed signals, was not my intention :/
Heh, no worries. I have an active imagination. I hope you won't hold it against me. 'Night, kiddo. Happy birthday. :)
Don't be silly. If anything I am flattered. Thanks again for coming :)
I don't think I'm going to make it tonight...a nasty chest thing has been making life miserable today. Probably just set my DVR and go to bed soon. No spoilers!
